{"tid":2402139,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"教育局：絕非教育下一代聽黨話 跟黨走 對有人抺黑深表遺憾","createTime":"2021-02-10T08:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-10T11:54:00.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ee13688e3a7b20efd22bd5a3586fec553d8b2f45","tid":2402139,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"教育局：通識科改革絕非政治洗腦 深信教師能掌握教學<br />\n<br />\n教育局發表文章，表示高中通識科改革是真正貫徹學科的初心，學生學習的課題是經過課程委員會的專業決定，絕非政治洗腦，深信教師能很快掌握新課程的教學工作。局方又批評有團體及個別人士，無視通識科多年來的異化問題，不但沒有提出具體改善建議，反而以立場先行，一向以既定立場詮釋課程，誤導視聽，將為學生福祉而進行的課程改革一再政治化，以情緒化字眼一再抺黑教育局，肆意挑撥教師與局方的互信，對此深表遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，新課程重視培養學生認識及認同國家及國民身分，與通識科一脈相承，教育業界應該不會陌生，批評有人錯誤引導，無視培養國民身分認同的合理性和必要性，漠視學生全面認識國家的需要。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2378650&d=9j7BdtwWq97OJFdF2FXGhdTdZGttzgfhyqIgu1GDYj0%3D&h=faafbb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2378650</a>"},{"pid":"3340569f44fbd029ebe0f54c2bf6081b1dd1c335","tid":2402139,"uid":39221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"聽習話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89672aebe809d0f933efe8e773742674bf52455a","tid":2402139,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"3340569f44fbd029ebe0f54c2bf6081b1dd1c335","tid":2402139,"uid":39221,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:45:07.000Z","msg":"聽習話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-10T08:45:35.000Z","msg":"聽維尼熊話 跟維尼走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"